Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.24,Bengoshi-Misaki_Cell,Cell,0,0,0,,Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:27.99,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.84,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Go to the cleaners and get my blouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.06,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:38.31,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You'll make it if you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.87,Bengoshi-White_Express,Sign,0,0,0,,Cleaning\N{\fs24\c&HD98B0F&}White Express
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:25.30,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:29.67,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I ran as fast as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but they had just closed the shutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:36.43,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to wear \Nto tomorrow's dinner party?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:38.24,Bengoshi-Overlap,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,{\a6}I-I understand, I'll get it \Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.71,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.47,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The dishes are piled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:34.86,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hey Kanae-chan, are you \Ngetting used to working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.79,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,380)}Office landlord: \NToyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.19,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Not at all, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.47,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,But I'm getting used to killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.47,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Hakamada's assistant:\N Nonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.16,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,There's no work to do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.54,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Temp:\N Shinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.29,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,There's no appointments\N today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.74,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hurry up and play your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.70,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,There, I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.51,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I didn't hear you say "Uno!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.65,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.04,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.19,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}The current episode's client:\N Ichikawa Tomohiro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:02:59.89,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:02.02,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,And I won fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.02,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You're on a winning streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.53,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Um... this is a law office, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.65,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,A client?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.86,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Are you a client?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.59,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.07,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Let me get your coat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.20,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Please, please, please. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.00,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sit. Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.98,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.10,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,We haven't had a male client in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.54,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Is it adultery? Did she cheat on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.06,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.17,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:47.33,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I am the attorney, Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.33,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Attorney: \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.37,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei, what are you doing? Get tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.15,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.54,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I think I'd better go somewhere elseー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:06.83,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,There, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.01,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I have work to doー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.55,Bengoshi-Overlap,K,0,0,0,,Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.82,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.46,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So you're being vexed by a monster wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,"Monster wife"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:23.69,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,A monster wife. A wife who \Nchanges after the wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.80,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,and menaces the husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:30.11,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Women are stronger than men nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.42,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Compared to women, these men are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.20,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,There are many kinds of monster wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.79,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,The visual type, mental type,\N and sexual type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.19,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What type is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.82,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:55.20,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm a marketer for a software company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.93,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,My wife is a homemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.31,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,She rarely does anything at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:05.48,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,But she has control over finances...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:15.22,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Tomohiro's wife: \NIchikawa Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.06,Bengoshi-Top,Misaki,0,0,0,,How long of a shower are you\N gonna take? What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.76,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,Gas bills aren't cheap, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:23.59,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,They cut your pay, \Nso think before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.91,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm cutting 5,000 yen from \Nyour allowance starting this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.10,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:33.53,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,10,000 yen a month isn't enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:38.62,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,There's no space left for me at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.44,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,She buys nothing but brand-name items...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,She goes to spas that cost \Nhundreds of thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.06,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,She goes out to lunches at first-rate hotels...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:54.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see... expenditures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is there any domestic violence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.91,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,As soon as she loses her temper,\N she resorts to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.55,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Recently she's learned a new technique: \Nthe roundhouse kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.26,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.21,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,So, she's the violent-type monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.59,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm at my wit's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:21.21,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,These days, when I get home from work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.22,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I get intensely anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.17,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I get frequent headaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.61,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Say, never mind that. \NWhat about adultery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.22,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Who's she cheating with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.79,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.49,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You know, your wife's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.46,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,As far as I know, she hasn't been cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.00,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What? She hasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:43.64,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.00,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.62,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.50,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:53.91,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Divorces not based on adultery\N can become prolonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.61,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Plus, it's difficult for a husband \Nto get compensation from a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:02.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It is a fact that women have \Nan advantage in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.42,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,This is quicksand. Quicksand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.73,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei, drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:12.74,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,He doesn't fit the bill, and who \Nknows if he can get compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We can get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.84,Default,All,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:24.75,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Compensation in a lawsuit based on the infliction\N of physical and psychological pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:30.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Domestic violence, moral harassment, \Nneglect of household duties, expenditures...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have all the premises \Nfor pursuing a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san, you truly \Nare in pain, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.97,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it is only proper that\Nwe demand compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:51.99,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N{\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:57.01,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption right,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Episode 4 \NThe Horror of the Monster Wife!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.97,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:06.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If you are ready to demand compensation, \Nthen I will give you my full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.53,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hey, what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.73,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:18.00,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,He accepted the client...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.18,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'm done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:24.27,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now that we've agreed, \Nlet's take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:29.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What would you want to tell \Nyour wife the most right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:37.31,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Close your eyes and \Nimagine your wife's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.79,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm cutting 5,000 yen from\N your allowance starting this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.65,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,The dishes are piled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,what do you want to say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.73,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.93,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! \NI'm doing the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:58.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let's go with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Go and let your wife take those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.41,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is what you're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.91,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Freelance Investigator: \NUmemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:12.39,Bengoshi-Top,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"Iron Spy Woman Marilyn" \Nseason 4, episode 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.85,Bengoshi-Spy_Marilyn,DVD box-set,0,0,0,,"Iron Spy Woman Marilyn"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:16.91,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,It depicts how Marilyn came \Nto possess a heart of iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.18,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,I'm not running anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.71,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,I won't run away ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:39.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,What did you mean when you told him \Nto let his wife take those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:44.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It will help him prepare \N to fight his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.18,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You'll find out shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.16,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm not running anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.47,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I won't run away ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.38,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm not running anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.36,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I won't run away ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.26,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm not running anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.40,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I won't run away ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.12,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.11,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.86,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.49,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.53,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:46.97,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm... doing the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.14,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,It was amazing how attractive\N she must have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.77,Default,All,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.86,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I told her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.79,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What an incredible monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This is beautiful, Ichikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.94,Bengoshi-Diagnosis_Report,Letters,0,0,0,,Diagnosis Report
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.94,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,This, and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,You knew this would happen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:41.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Anyway, now we have proof \Nof domestic violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You've cleared the first hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.05,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:49.46,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:53.49,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the second stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.58,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.57,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When you battle a monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:04.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you must attack its vital points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.94,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Vital points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:23.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You must thoroughly uncover\N the facts of your wife's expenditures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Gather as much evidence as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:30.07,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Purchased items, receipts, \Ncredit card statements...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.46,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And savings account ledger\N would be helpful, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.64,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:09.51,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I knocked it over by accident\Nso I'm cleaning it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What is important here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:21.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,is establishing the ratio of your wife's\N expenditures to your income.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,These things will be evidence \Nfor the expenditures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.47,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Now to find the savings ledger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.29,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,620,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.78,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.23,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,At most, we had about \Nsix million in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Six million...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, she spent it all on this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.93,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Look at all that stuff she bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.63,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I had no idea we were so depleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.90,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Could your wife have \Nanother savings account?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.13,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.67,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,We've closed out our \Ncertificates of deposit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.41,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.04,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You can't get any \Ncompensation with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.42,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That's why I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:05.29,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,If it's not possible, I can \Nforgo the compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:14.74,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I knew you were acting sneaky lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.22,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,and look what I've found...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:23.49,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You got my ledger and are \Ntalking to a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.14,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You trying to separate from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.62,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,A woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.36,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You have a new woman, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.93,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.82,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.73,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Who is the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.75,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:43.19,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Say it! Confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.16,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I am not cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.49,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.49,Bengoshi-Overlap,K,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I know I might be \Ncrossing a line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Your husband isn't cheating on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.41,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're the lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh. The bread's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:23.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Have some if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.07,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I won't agree to a separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:39.12,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,But, if you insist we separate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:42.01,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I want ten million yen \Nin compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.75,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What is the premise \Nfor the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Has your husband done something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.71,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Of course. Our marriage is sexless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.26,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,None whatsoever, from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:58.36,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,This man is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:03.26,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Sensei. I have reason \Nfor divorce, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:07.90,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Yes. In the case a man is impotent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.49,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm not impotent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.81,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I can get it up for anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.75,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,So, you {\i1}are{\i0} cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.02,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Confess! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:28.18,Bengoshi-Overlap,Misaki,0,0,0,,Madam, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.23,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Say it. Get it out. Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please eat this and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.10,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.04,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:42.40,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll never agree to a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,You, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.54,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:13.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She said my bagel is disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.70,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san. I will\N assuredly get you a divorce,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and compensation, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.37,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Looks like she pressed the right button.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.08,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,He's just bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,What the hell just came\Ndashing out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.86,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That's the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,It finally reared its ugly head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:42.82,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Is it possible that I'd get billed \Nfor compensation instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:45.57,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You weren't cheating on her, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do such a thing,\N I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,Getting compensation might be \Nimpossible this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.25,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That's right. There have no savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.05,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:02.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She might have no savings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:05.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but she can't escape the \Nobligation to make compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.48,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,If she has no money, \Nhow would she pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:17.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Upon the divorce agreement, she simply must \Nacknowledge the obligation for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:19.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She has ten years to make \Nthe full compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In other words, even if she can't \Npay now, after the divorce,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:26.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,we can demand any income \Nshe earns after the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.30,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Even after ten years, \Nthere can be another hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:36.51,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,520)}Compensation Timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:36.51,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,520)}Normally three years, but can be extended to 10 years \Nat the time of divorce agreement. (If there is another trial,\N it can be prolonged another 10 more years)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.64,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,at which time, she would be
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:35.77,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,given another ten years to \Nmake the full compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.55,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.70,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.17,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What an exhausting thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:46.71,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Let that monster suffer for \Nten years, for twenty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:51.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, this time around, \Nwe're taking a faster route.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.61,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:59.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san, are you familiar \Nwith property distribution?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.41,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:07.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Halving of assets on occasion of divorce \Nis standard practice of property distribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:12.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,regardless of who initiates the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.18,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:20.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Therefore, we deduct the \Ncompensation from this half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.91,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:26.10,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,The assets are close \Nto zero to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:31.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The term "assets" does not\Nonly refer to savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The biggest asset between you two \Nis your condominium, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.99,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:43.08,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,So she has an asset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:47.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When the condominium gets sold, \Neven after the remaining loan is paid off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,there should be some left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:55.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Half of it is supposed \Nto go to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:21:02.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In that case, we take our \Ncompensation from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:16.28,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,520)}When the other party is a housewife
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:16.28,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,520)}Compensation can be taken out of the property distribution.  It is essential to elucidate the details carefully in the divorce agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.03,Bengoshi-Top,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.42,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Good job, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:13.32,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, Ichikawa-san, let's \Nmove on to the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:16.16,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have to draft a divorce agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:19.09,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, will you please \Nhelp with the drafting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:25.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san. We're finally \Nabout to reach the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.09,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.88,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I will leave it in your capable hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, there's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We need to make a first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.27,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kurumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:44.95,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We need to teach that \Nselfish monster a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:49.73,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,Make my day, monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:07.40,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Thank you. You're all so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:10.78,Default,Akiyo,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \NYou're good, too, Ichikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.98,Default,All,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:16.58,Default,W,0,0,0,,I know, and I'm even \Ntaking karaoke lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:21.12,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should take classes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:24.58,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,But I have tea ceremony and koto lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:27.61,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm so busy every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.19,Default,All,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:31.30,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:36.50,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san, you haven't \Ntouched your drink at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:39.98,Default,All,0,0,0,,That's right. Come on. Let's drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:45.11,Default,LadYoshie,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san, what are \Nyou singing next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:47.77,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Oh... then, Beyonce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:50.30,Default,All,0,0,0,,Beyonce?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:52.90,Default,All,0,0,0,,I love Beyonce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.21,Default,All,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.15,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm paying for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:01.70,Default,Person,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Ichikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:05.24,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll pay the tab next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.81,Default,All,0,0,0,,Thanks, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:07.76,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:09.09,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.31,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Miss, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.02,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,It appears your card has been declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:17.86,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What? That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.82,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Would you like to pay with cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:22.22,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.39,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.70,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'll pick up the tab today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:29.84,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:30.93,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:34.71,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.66,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Why aren't you answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.96,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:14.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, let's keep a log of anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:15.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,that could lead to further disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:16.69,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:27.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know how frustrated you must feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:30.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,I was like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:32.30,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.75,0:24:37.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,I got divorced just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:42.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:44.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,And now I can look forward to future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:46.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.36,0:24:50.32,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:52.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,He's a strange man, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.25,0:25:04.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have an appraisal of \NIchikawa-san's condominium.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:09.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In total, it comes out to \N35 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:16.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Deducting the loan payback from that,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.21,0:25:17.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it comes out to 14 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.13,0:25:24.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Seven million will be paid to your \Nwife in the property distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:26.63,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's quite a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.44,0:25:31.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We will bill her for the entire amount,\N for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.01,0:25:35.10,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Seven million... the entire amount?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.19,0:25:38.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You could say she's getting off cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.03,0:25:41.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You earned that money with your \Nblood, sweat, and tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.33,0:25:45.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but your wife spent \Nit all for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:51.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This amount represents not only that, \Nbut also the great suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.54,0:25:53.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that you have endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.61,0:25:57.00,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, let's get compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.49,0:26:11.80,Bengoshi-Misaki_Calls,Cell historYoshie,0,0,0,,Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.44,0:26:21.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.85,0:26:27.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now, it's time to clearly express \Nyour intent to divorce to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.31,0:26:31.55,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.60,0:26:34.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.52,0:26:39.61,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Well, yes... to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.59,0:26:45.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Your fear will become money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:50.50,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,My fear... will become money...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:55.44,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, let's announce your intent \Nto divorce with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.98,0:27:07.92,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Vertical_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada\N Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.58,0:27:07.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ichikawa-san is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.92,0:27:10.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better for him\N to quietly divorce her,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.19,0:27:14.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,instead of trying to get compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.43,0:27:18.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,People subjected to domestic violence\N and moral harassment for long periods
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.21,0:27:23.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,often come to believe that \Nthey are weak people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.31,0:27:27.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And they have a tendency \Nto rely on the perpetrators.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.11,0:27:33.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can relate, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.38,0:27:35.40,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's essential for \NIchikawa-san right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.85,0:27:41.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,is for him to reclaim his former self.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.17,0:27:57.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,To do that, he must also \Ndemand compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.20,0:28:09.08,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Is all this that so-called\N Hakamada's idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.52,0:28:13.46,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You put a stop on my card, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.97,0:28:22.56,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea \Nhow humiliated I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:26.16,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.61,0:28:29.10,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:33.57,Bengoshi-Flashback,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, let's announce your intent \Nto divorce with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:49.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please divorce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.41,0:28:59.53,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.59,0:29:04.56,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:14.67,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,like to separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.84,0:29:42.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.42,0:29:48.67,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,As you said, Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.96,0:29:51.11,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I told her with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.11,0:29:55.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,She said she'll keep me\N as her pet until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.34,0:29:57.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.81,0:30:05.21,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,But, I feel like I was finally \Nable to look her in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.64,0:30:10.66,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's the first I've seen you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.77,0:30:13.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.11,0:30:19.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Because all I can do is help \Nyou with the legal aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.59,0:30:24.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It is you who must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:28.29,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.60,0:30:42.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have come here today
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.19,0:30:47.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,to ask your consent in divorcing your \Nhusband, Ichikawa Tomohiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.70,0:30:51.93,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You guys just don't let up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.93,0:30:53.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:30:58.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Misaki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.52,0:31:01.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,over the past five years, \Nyou have spent five million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.95,0:31:07.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,of your husband's hard-earned money \Non expensive brand-name items, beauty treatments,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.41,0:31:09.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and extravagant dinners \Nwith your high-society friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:12.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Not to mention domestic violence...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.69,0:31:18.46,Bengoshi-Diagnosis_Report2,Letter,0,0,0,,Diagnosis Report
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.03,0:31:14.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Verbal abuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.91,0:31:18.46,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.20,0:31:20.59,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:23.15,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.01,0:31:25.24,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Misaki,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.59,0:31:31.14,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm doing the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.33,0:31:39.80,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Misaki,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're \Ntalking to, you piece of trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.16,0:31:42.19,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.19,0:31:44.71,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Misaki,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten how to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.04,0:31:47.82,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Misaki,0,0,0,,Get on your knees and beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.82,0:31:52.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Demanding that someone get on their knees \Nagainst their will can be considered illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.99,0:31:55.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If you still insist you're \Nnot the perpetrator
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.53,0:31:58.00,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,with sufficient reason for divorce,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:32:00.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,then we will have to \Ntake matters to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.08,0:32:06.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Even in court, I assure you, they \Nwill decide in favor of the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.20,0:32:08.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.03,0:32:13.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you will be billed to compensate your husband's\Npsychological and physical anguish,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.96,0:32:18.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,as well as repayment for your personal expenditures.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.66,0:32:21.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The total will be seven million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.62,0:32:24.36,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Seven million?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.36,0:32:26.45,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.45,0:32:28.89,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You saw my bank ledger, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.28,0:32:32.36,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.19,0:32:37.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Here is the appraisal \Nof this condominium.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.27,0:32:39.07,Bengoshi-Appraisal_Report,PapeRina,0,0,0,,Condominium Appraisal Report
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.02,0:32:41.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Out of the sum you will receive \Nfrom the sale of the condominium,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:46.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,by property distribution, \None half will become yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.08,0:32:51.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In other words, you are \Nentitled to one half
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.29,0:32:57.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,of 14 million yen after the divorce, \Nand paying back the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.44,0:33:03.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Therefore, you will be paying \Nzero out of pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.74,0:33:06.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Misaki-san, how lucky for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.89,0:33:09.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that you won't have to dig \Ninto your own savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:14.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.86,0:33:19.95,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'll say it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:21.78,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I said I won't agree to a divorce!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.78,0:33:24.28,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Stamp and sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:25.22,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.22,0:33:26.46,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Please set me free!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.46,0:33:27.59,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.05,0:33:30.71,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If you will not agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.71,0:33:33.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,then we have no choice \Nbut to take it to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.75,0:33:39.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,However, if it comes down to that, \Nthere will be court fees, attorney fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.65,0:33:43.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,in which case, in all eventuality, your \Nsettlement will be next to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:46.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.25,0:33:50.65,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.65,0:33:52.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why do you not want to divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.81,0:33:57.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You wanted your husband's \Nattention, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.15,0:34:04.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have done some investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.59,0:34:09.07,Bengoshi-Flashback,Staff,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.92,0:34:12.36,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,Um... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.36,0:34:15.29,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We have to \Nhave each other's backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.29,0:34:19.69,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kurumi,0,0,0,,But, it's not easy to associate \Nwith people like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.69,0:34:21.42,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kurumi,0,0,0,,All the money in the \Nworld won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.42,0:34:23.60,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.41,0:34:31.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Misaki-san, you were lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.52,0:34:34.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Since you've moved into \N this condominium,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.38,0:34:37.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you've had no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.96,0:34:43.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,On top of that, your husband has \Nbeen working overtime until late.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.39,0:34:51.00,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And it was in this situation that \Nyou met the local high-society wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.57,0:34:53.49,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.83,0:34:55.23,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,This? It's from Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.23,0:34:55.77,Bengoshi-Flashback,W2,0,0,0,,From Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.77,0:34:58.14,Bengoshi-Flashback,W3,0,0,0,,Did you go to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.52,0:35:05.39,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.39,0:35:07.80,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:09.75,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,This is my favorite handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.75,0:35:11.40,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.40,0:35:13.07,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.47,0:35:13.05,Bengoshi-Flashback_Overlap,Misaki,0,0,0,,Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.11,0:35:16.17,Bengoshi-Flashback,W1,0,0,0,,Wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.17,0:35:22.33,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That started the deepening of your \Nrelationship with those women...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.33,0:35:28.43,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Hakamada,0,0,0,,However, the money it took to \Nassociate with them was exorbitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.74,0:35:33.81,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But you didn't want to leave \Nyour new friends behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.39,0:35:38.07,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and you continued seeing them, \Nthough you didn't have the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.75,0:35:44.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The expenditures became \Na matter of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.44,0:35:47.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but you couldn't stop yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.94,0:35:52.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You wanted to confide\N in your husband, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.55,0:35:59.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But instead, your attitude toward \Nhim became increasingly cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.25,0:36:02.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and kept escalating.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.85,0:36:09.07,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.31,0:36:15.15,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Is that true? Because if it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.95,0:36:18.77,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.24,0:36:20.85,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.85,0:36:23.62,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What do you know about me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.62,0:36:26.22,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Do you think you're some TV detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.22,0:36:33.08,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I worked hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.67,0:36:34.78,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.70,0:36:38.71,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I wanted you to have a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:39.88,Bengoshi-Overlap,Misaki,0,0,0,,I said, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.95,0:36:43.61,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.87,0:36:47.91,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.61,0:36:51.83,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,If you were lonely, \Nwhy didn't you just say so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.24,0:36:54.83,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,If keeping up appearances was difficult,\N why didn't you speak up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.81,0:36:57.62,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.12,0:37:01.34,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.49,0:37:06.96,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I told you over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:13.35,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,Honey, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.35,0:37:18.04,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,I don't know if I like \Nthis condominium...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.91,0:37:21.43,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,This subject again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:24.52,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,This is an important time for me.\N I might get promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.52,0:37:26.05,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I don't have time to move elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.52,0:37:30.18,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misaki,0,0,0,,But, Tomohiro, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.18,0:37:34.26,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Sorry, but let's talk \Nabout it some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:43.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Nonetheless, you have vexed your \Nhusband for many long years,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:46.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and for that, you will have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.40,0:37:49.54,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Your guilt is not expunged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.54,0:37:50.70,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.70,0:37:52.66,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:58.48,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,If you want a divorce\N that badly, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.31,0:38:29.53,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.60,0:38:54.17,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.82,0:38:58.94,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,If only I had been more \Nattentive to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.17,0:39:13.12,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Misaki. Let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.23,0:39:19.91,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,I now know, that I'm the one \Nthat turned you into a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.89,0:39:28.74,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,...because I kept running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.03,0:39:38.67,Default,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Let's start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.51,0:39:45.55,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.65,0:39:55.57,Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.57,0:40:19.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.51,0:40:22.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Um... Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.25,0:40:24.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.57,0:40:30.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,You knew this was going \Nto happen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.95,0:40:35.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,I think you knew how it \Nwas all going to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.67,0:40:40.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,All I did was clean \Nup the contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.63,0:40:44.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She said she wouldn't divorce, \Nwhile saying their marriage was sexless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:47.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She never took off her wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.43,0:40:52.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Misaki-san was full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.55,0:40:59.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.49,0:41:22.58,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,I would've never guessed \Nyou could do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.58,0:41:27.49,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,there are ways to get compensation \Nfrom housewives without income.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.49,0:41:29.33,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I was surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.21,0:41:34.85,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Monster wives really \Ndo exist, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:37.07,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,Five years from now, \Nyou will become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.07,0:41:39.43,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.29,0:41:43.14,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.14,0:41:44.96,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.96,0:41:46.73,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.73,0:41:49.63,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,Because I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.61,0:41:51.53,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.07,0:41:57.19,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.34,0:42:00.11,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.36,0:42:08.62,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.62,0:42:13.06,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Are you saying Hakamada-sensei didn't \Nget compensation fees this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.28,0:42:22.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.94,0:42:26.67,Default,V1,0,0,0,,Sensei, we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.94,0:42:36.21,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.67,0:42:30.04,Default,V2,0,0,0,,There's a line of people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.14,0:42:30.04,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Diagonal,Caption,0,0,0,,The Hakamada Law Office{\c&H1C99D3&} in great peril?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.04,0:42:32.58,Default,W1,0,0,0,,My husband is cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.58,0:42:36.21,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,A controlling wife, traditional man, wrestler woman:
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.58,0:42:36.22,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We can't get compensation \Nfor such a minor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.54,0:42:36.21,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,Hakamada in a big crisis!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.22,0:42:38.05,Bengoshi-Top,All,0,0,0,,I will never fail to get compensated!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.28,0:42:39.92,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(340,0)}This drama is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.05,0:42:39.39,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's going on here?

